pageProduct.name: The Natural Confectionery Co. Fruit Chews 180g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

The Natural Confectionery Co. Fruity Chews. Have fun with your friends & fam with our did you know wrapper questions!

The Natural Confectionery Co. Fruity Chews are tutti fruity, deliciously juicy! Packed full of deliciousness, with no artificial colours, no artificial flavours, no GMOs and no artificial sweeteners.

Have fun with your friends and fam with our DID YOU KNOW wrapper questions whilst you dig into our yummy fruit flavours: Strawberry, Lemon, Orange, Raspberry, Blackcurrant

Product Claims: No artificial colours, flavours and sweetener. No GMO, no high fructose corn syrup

Size: 180g

Flavour: Strawberry, lemon, orange, raspberry, blackcurrant

Serving Size: 25g (approx. 3 chews)

Servings Per Pack: 7.2

Warnings

Not all varieties of chews may be contained in this pack.

Ingredients

Cane Sugar, Glucose Syrup, Vegetable Oil, Food Acid (Citric), Fruit Juice Concentrates, Gelatine, Natural Flavours, Natural Food Colours (Anthocyanins, Grape Skin Extract, Paprika Oleoresin, Turmeric).

Allergen Free From: Artificial Colours| Artificial Flavours

Directions

Please store in cool, dry conditions.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Wrap. Return to store. arl.org.au | Red Cycle. In Australia, this packaging is recyclable through the REDcycle Program. www.redcycle.net.au

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
